data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
1. Fill out all the textboxes on the left. If you are unsure about ones action, hover your mouse over it. 2. Add evidence by pressing the obvious "+" button. 3. To edit existing evidence, you can click on the icon of the evidence. Right click to delete. You can see the title of the evidence if you hover over the icon. 4. To export, click the "export button". To load a case, click the "Load" button. If you don't really know what you are doing, and the program is in the same folder with the client tick "EasyExport" However, if you want to save the case ini in a custom destination, do not tick "EasyExport" 5. Launch AO2, go to a Courtroom and on the OCC(chat box on the far right) type the following commands: /cm /load_case (title)
If you have any questions feel free to contact me @Cents02
